      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What is the best Scrabble gift for a beginner?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "For beginners, a classic Scrabble set paired with the Official Scrabble Players Dictionary (OSPD6) makes an ideal gift. The dictionary helps new players learn valid words and builds confidence. Budget around $30-40 for both items together." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What should I buy for a tournament Scrabble player?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Tournament players appreciate premium tile bags (velvet drawstring), a chess clock for timed games, the Collins Scrabble Words book, or a subscription to a word study app like Zyzzyva. Avoid novelty items — competitive players prefer functional gear that improves their game." }
      }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pt-4 pb-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1">
        <a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
        <span class="mx-1">›</span>
        <a href="/blog/beginner-guides/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors text-gray-300">Beginner Guides</a>
      </nav>

      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Best Scrabble Gifts 2026: Gift Guide for Word Game Lovers</h1>

      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-20">June 20, 2026</time>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <span>9 min read</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔍</span> Solver</a> <a href="/activities/#quiz" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🎯</span> Quiz</a> <a href="/activities/#anagram" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔀</span> Anagram</a> <a href="/activities/#rack" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🎲</span> Rack</a> <a href="/activities/#wotd" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">📖</span> WOTD</a> <a href="/sixty-seconds/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">⏱️</span> 60s</a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">
        Searching for the perfect gift for a Scrabble enthusiast? Whether they are a casual kitchen-table player or a competitive tournament regular, this guide covers the best Scrabble gifts across every category and budget. From premium rotating boards to word study apps, here are the top picks for 2026.
      </p>

      <!-- Hero Card: #1 Gift Pick -->
      <div class="not-prose my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-500/50 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-950/30 to-yellow-950/20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500/70">👑 #1 Gift Pick</div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">DELUXE ROTATING BOARD</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-300 font-semibold mb-3">$80–$100 · Spins 360° · Raised tile grid · Premium wood finish</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">The Winning Solutions Deluxe Rotating Scrabble Board is the standout gift for 2026. The built-in lazy-susan lets each player spin the board to face them without disturbing tiles. Raised grid edges prevent tiles from sliding, and the solid wood construction looks stunning on any table. It is the single gift that impresses every time.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stat Strip -->
      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">25+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Gift Ideas</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">$5–$200</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Price Range</p></div>
