          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Apps, subscriptions, and online tournament entries.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-500/30 bg-red-950/10">
          <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">👕 Clothing & Fun</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">T-shirts, mugs, tile jewelry, and novelty items.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/10">
          <p class="text-blue-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🎁 Stocking Stuffers</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Under $15 — mini games, magnets, keychains, and card sets.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Best Scrabble Boards</h2>

      <p>A quality board transforms the playing experience. The right board depends on where and how often they play. Here are the top picks by category.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Deluxe Rotating Board ($80–$100):</span> The gold standard. Lazy-susan base, raised grid, wood finish. Perfect for dedicated players who host game nights regularly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Classic Board ($20–$30):</span> The original flat board with plastic tiles. Affordable, familiar, and perfect for families and casual players who want the authentic experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Travel Scrabble ($15–$25):</span> Magnetic or snap-fit tiles on a compact folding board. Ideal for road trips, flights, and vacations. Tiles stay put even on bumpy surfaces.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Giant Garden Scrabble ($100–$200):</span> Oversized outdoor board with large wooden tiles. A showpiece for garden parties and summer gatherings. Weather-resistant versions available.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Tile Accessories</h2>

      <p>Accessories elevate the playing experience without replacing the board. These are the gifts that serious players actually use every game.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10">
          <p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🎒 Premium Tile Bag</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Velvet drawstring bag with wide opening. $10–$20. Essential for tournament players.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10">
          <p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">⏱️ Chess Clock</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Digital timer for timed games. $20–$40. Makes games faster and more competitive.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10">
          <p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">📋 Score Pads</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Pre-formatted scoring sheets. $8–$12 for 100 sheets. Beats scrap paper every time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10">
          <p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🔲 Wooden Tile Racks</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Solid hardwood racks with grooved slots. $15–$25 for a set of 4. Upgrade from flimsy plastic.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Word List Books</h2>

      <p>For players who want to improve, books remain the most effective study tool. The right book depends on their level and which dictionary they play with.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Dictionary Tip</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">North American players use <span class="text-white font-medium">TWL (Tournament Word List)</span> while international players use <span class="text-white font-medium">SOWPODS/Collins</span>. Make sure you buy the right one for your recipient's region.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Official Scrabble Players Dictionary (OSPD6) — $15:</span> The standard reference for home and club play in North America. Contains all valid 2-to-8 letter words with brief definitions. Perfect for beginners and casual players.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Collins Scrabble Words — $20:</span> The international tournament dictionary with 280,000+ words. Essential for anyone playing in SOWPODS tournaments or online against international opponents.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Word Freak by Stefan Fatsis — $12:</span> The definitive narrative book about competitive Scrabble culture. Part memoir, part journalism — follows the author from casual player to tournament competitor. Entertaining for any word game fan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Digital Gifts</h2>

      <p>For the tech-savvy word game player, digital gifts offer infinite replay value. These subscriptions and apps help players study, practice, and compete from anywhere.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">📱 <a href="https://zyzzyva.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:underline">Zyzzyva Word Study</a></p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Free desktop app for word list study with flashcard drills, quizzes, and anagram practice. The #1 study tool for competitive players.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🎮 Online Tournament Entry</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Gift a tournament registration ($25–$50). Platforms like <a href="https://woogles.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-green-300 hover:underline">Woogles.io</a> host rated online events weekly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
