          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🔍 <a href="/" class="hover:underline">ScrabbleWordsFinder.com</a></p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Free online word finder with instant results. Bookmark it for them — no sign-up, no cost, unlimited use.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Stocking Stuffers Under $15</h2>

      <p>Small budget? These affordable gifts still delight word game fans. Perfect for Secret Santa, stocking stuffers, or add-on presents.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
