        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
          <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🃏 Scrabble Card Game</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Scrabble Slam or Scrabble Dash — fast card versions. $8–$12. Great for travel.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
          <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">☕ Scrabble Tile Mug</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Mug with their name spelled in Scrabble tiles. $12–$15. Personalizable online.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Related Articles -->
